title: Jack Harlow & Druski Talk Comedies, Pick Up Lines, Movies & More | GOAT Talk with Complex
author: Complex
description:
On this episode of GOAT Talk, Jack Harlow and Druski discuss GOAT liquor, Druski skits, chains in hip-hop, sex positions, vacation spots, and more. GOAT Talk, a new show where we ask today's greats to crown their all-time greats.

Read the full Complex digital cover story here: https://stories.complex.com/jack-harlow-druski-interview-2021-cover-story/
